query:
SELECT ta.tutorId, COUNT(*) as slot_count, u.name as tutor_name 
FROM tutor_availability ta 
LEFT JOIN users u ON ta.tutorId = u.id 
GROUP BY ta.tutorId 
LIMIT 5;
